protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Redevelopment of the site to provide 125 residential units, 513 sqm of commercial floor space (use classes A1, A2, A3, B1 or D1), ranging from 4 to 14-storeys and a stand-alone commercial unit; 24 car parking spaces (including car club and accessible provision), private and communal landscaped amenity areas, secure cycle parking and other associated development.
